Author: heavenlessly
Text: oh jeez..:( wow i never ever thought i would have any kind of disordered eating. i mean, i have always been a very picky eater but as i got older, i realized i was losing weight and i just..liked it. i think i was subconsciously doing all of this and being so picky and having so many rules because i liked the way i feel when im not full and when im empty and in control of how i feel. huh..well..this was an unfortunate revelation.

Author: lupiini
Text: Yeah it does sound like an eating disorder, you should definitely seek help for it.
